comment: Dedmon (ORL) runs through Lowry (TOR) as he sets a legal screen.
Fournier (ORL) makes incidental contact that does not affect DeRozan's (TOR) RSBQ.
Fournier (ORL) makes body to body contact with DeRozan (TOR) that causes him to lose the ball.
Harris (ORL) moves his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Carroll (TOR) makes contact to Harris' (ORL) arm and body that affects his jump shot.
Fournier (ORL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends DeRozan's (TOR) drive to the basket.
Dedmon (ORL) makes body to body contact with DeRozan (TOR) that affects his shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) sets the screen on Fournier (ORL) and does not give him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
RHH shows Fournier (ORL) cleanly strips the ball from DeRozan (TOR).
Smith (ORL) pushes Valanciunas (TOR) as he starts his play to the basket.
Oladipo (ORL) pushes Lowry (TOR) in the back and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Joseph (TOR) commits a clear path foul on Oladipo (ORL) on the fast break.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a clear path foul was upheld.
Carroll (TOR) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
